sp.p:
That's right wench ! Give me a kiss. Thérèse shall give you a lift, when she comes in. Now,
      Edouard, darling ; quick! run and get your new sash—and let's make you smart— and you, girls;
      run away and each bring me a bouquet here in ten minutes time.

Well, I don't care, I say still, it's a sad thing to see such a lovely young woman pining
      for a husband, when there are so many to be had for the asking; but I suppose you are right;
      there being no proof she's a widow, there's but one thing left for me to do.
